sys_hub_action_type_definition.description:
The Certificate Inventory and Management module does not currently support the discovery of CSC-issued assets such as domains.
This new Action helps address that gap by enabling the retrieval of domain portfolio data directly from CSC.
sys_hub_action_type_definition.name: Get Stored Domains from CSC
